short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Web based softphone to be used for existing Maxsip customers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Softphone can be used instead of your desk phone to place and receive calls. 

You can send and receive sms/mms messages (if your extension has been configured for SMS).

You must be a Maxsip customer to use this app.
